^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|There were some issues with the play, but I want to focus on Roberta's balancing first. Basically, if they have an 8+ card fit, and have voluntarily stopped at the 2 level, you should always try to push them higher if at all possible. When it goes 1H-P-2H, they have a known 8 card fit at least. And then when I pass, you know that the points are approximately equal between each side.|
