NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The reason for "if they have a fit, you have a fit" is, if you are short in their suit, mathematically, you must be long in some other suit. The  bottom line is if it goes 1x-p-2x-p-p, you should almost always balance in the pass out seat. And Roberta has the perfect balancing double hand--3 diamonds with their 9 card fit is a very nice contract.|
