NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|One comment on the defense. Ann, you should rarely trump when you have a natural trump trick. In particular when Don led a spade off dummy, there was no reason for you to trump. Same with club. You are just giving away a trick. At worst, if Don wins the trick you are just trading and if it turns out Roberta can win the trick (which she could in spades), you gave up a trick.|
