^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, excellent bidding on this hand. Let's count Bergen points. After 1S, lets look at Pam's Dummy Points. She has 13 HCP, minus one for Jx of hearts, plus two length points, plus one for quality suit in diamonds, and plus 3 for singleton with 4 card trump support for a total of 18 Dummy Points. Therefore, she has a clear 3S bid, which shows 17-19 Bergen Points. |
