NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Next, let's count Dee's declarer points. She has 12 HCP, plus two length points for 14 Starting Points. Once Pam supports spades, she can add two points for the singleton, and an extra point for the 4+ card heart side suit which comes to 17 Declarer Points. Therefore, if they have enough key cards, they should be in six, as they have a minimum combined count of 34. |
