NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|You need 33 to explore for slam. However, once they discover they are missing one key card and the Queen of spades, they should settle for 5. As I said, six happens to make on this hand, but in the long run 5 will be a better contract than six. You should only bid a small slam if you have all the key cards, or 4 key cards plus the Queen of trumps.|
